2. If not in registry: `npm search mcp-server-{service}`
3. Run quality check (maintained? >100 downloads? `uvx snyk-agent-scan@latest` passes? — Snyk Agent Scan, PyPI; full verdict needs `SNYK_TOKEN`)
4. If passes, add to `.cursor/mcp.json` and `.mcp.json` with pinned version and security annotations
5. Run `/discover-mcp` for a full dependency scan
